mentor-element elementor-element-16d35d3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"16d35d3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Life can change quickly. Long-Term Care Planning helps you stay in control if daily activities become difficult after an illness or injury. With clear, flexible options, you can line up support for in-home help or a care facility without disrupting your family\u2019s routine. Our team designs a plan that fits your preferences, budget, and goals.</span></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6f461fda\" data-id=\"6f461fda\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9401fe1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9401fe1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://advancedbenefitdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/senior-couple-analyzing-their-savings-while-going-through-home-finances-1024x683.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-230\" alt=\"Tax-Free Retirement\" srcset=\"https://advancedbenefitdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/senior-couple-analyzing-their-savings-while-going-through-home-finances-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://advancedbenefitdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/senior-couple-analyzing-their-savings-while-going-through-home-finances-300x200.jpg 300w, https://advancedbenefitdesigns.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/s